   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COLOMBIA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Core funding supports the OHCHR in Colombia in their vital support of the human rights elements of the Colombian peace accords in 2020-2021. In addition to the specific tasks mandated for OHCHR Colombia in the peace accord, the Office will continue with its work of monitoring and reporting on human rights violations; protection of HRDs; supporting Colombian institutions to develop legislation and systems implementing international human rights norms; supporting victims, indigenous, Afro-Colombian and other civil society actors to vindicate their rights under Colombian law, including land, water and environmental rights; and facilitating public apologies and collective reparation by FARC and other armed actors in communities affected by the conflict.</narrative>
  </description>
